ACF085E3497639C23CB0ECAAA292FC16: Applies post process effects to the camera.

Determines the game phases during which the device will be enabled.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.AppliesToClass.Desc: Determines which Class can activate the device and be affected by the post process effect.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.AppliesToTeam.Descr: Determines which Team can activate the device and be affected by the post process effect.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.DisableForAll.Descr: Disables the device for all players. Pauses ongoing blending until reenabled.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.DisableForInstigato: Disables the device only for this instigator. Pauses ongoing blending until reeenabled.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.EnableForAll.Descri: Enables the device for all players.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.EnableForInstigator: Enables the device only for this instigator.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.EffectDuration.Desc: How long the post process effect will last before automatically blending out. Infinite duration (0) will stay active until disabled or manually blended out.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.BlendInStrength.Des: How strong the chosen post process effect is when blended in.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.StartingStrength.De: How strong the chosen post process effect is when first enabled. Clamps to Blend In Strength.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.Priority.Descriptio: If multiple Post Process Devices overlap determines which active effect will display. Effects with the same priority will attempt to blend together.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.ResetForAll.Descrip: Resets to the initial starting strength for all players. Ends any ongoing blending.
Resets to the initial starting strength only for the instigator. Ends any ongoing blending.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.OnBlendingInIsCompl: Sends an event to linked devices when blending in is complete.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.OnBlendingOutIsComp: Sends an event to linked devices when blending out is complete.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.BlendInForInstigato: Starts blending in only for this instigator.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.BlendOutForInstigat: Starts blending out only for this instigator.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.BlendInForAll.Descr: Starts the Blend In from current strength to the Blend In Strength value for all players.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.BlendOutForAll.Desc: Starts the Blend Out from current strength to 0 strength for all players.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.BlendInDuration.Des: The amount of time it takes to go from 0 Strength to Blend In Strength.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.BlendOutDuration.De: The amount of time it takes to go from Blend In Strength to 0 Strength .
UserOptionDefinition.Device_PostProcess_C.PostProcessEffect.D: The post process effect to apply when enabled.
